      parameter (raddeg = 180 / pi)
      complex*16 coni
      parameter (coni = (0,1))
c     kf = fa/rs with fa = (9*pi/4)**third, see Ash&Merm, pg 37
      parameter (fa = 1.919 158 292 677 512 811d0)

